Package: ggtriangles
Type: Package
Title: Implements geom_triangles
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christian Testa
Maintainer: Christian Testa <testa101@gmail.com>
Description: ggtriangles provides the geom_triangles function, a ggplot2 
  geom layer which will plot the x,y data provided as triangles with 
  height given by argument z. 
